<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA523_08_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema523_su_08.css" />
  <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema523_08_0004.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_08_su_0004 paging">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_pink">
          <div>
              <span lang="y">점대칭도형에서 대응점끼리 이은 선분과 대칭의 중심 사이의 관계를 알아봅시다.</span>
              <button type="button" class="icon_supplies" lang="y" data-supplies="pop_supplies_area_1">준비물</button>
          </div>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <div class="pop_area pop_supplies_area pop_supplies_area_1">
      <div class="supplies_zoom_wrap">
        <button type="button" class="close"></button>
        <div class="supplies_zoom scrollable">
          <div class="supplies_box_wrap">
            <div class="supplies_box">
              <div class="supplies_tit">삼각자, 각도기, 자</div>
              <div class="supplies_contents">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_08_SU/0004_supplies.png" alt="준비물 도형" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="controller">
            <button class="supplies_scale_down" disabled></button>
            <button class="supplies_scale_up"></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <article class="page page_1">
        <h3 lang="y">대응점끼리 각각 선분으로 이어 보세요.​</h3>
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="figure_img_box">
            <div class="figure">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_08_SU/0004_content.svg" alt="도형이미지">
              <div class="figure_triangle">
                <span class="txt_1" lang="y">ㄱ</span>
                <span class="txt_2" lang="y">ㄴ</span>
                <span class="txt_3" lang="y">ㄷ</span>
                <span class="txt_4" lang="y">ㄹ</span>
                <span class="txt_5" lang="y">ㅁ</span>
                <span class="txt_6" lang="y">ㅂ</span>
              </div>
              <div class="connect_box_wrap">
                <div class="connect_wrap_click connect_wrap" data-connections="[]" data-answer-single='[["s1","e3"],["s2","e2"],["s3","e1"]]' data-sample-line='[["s1","e1"],["s2","e2"],["s3","e3"]]' data-mode='single'>
                    <div class="start_group">
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="s1"></div>
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="s2"></div>
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="s3"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="end_group">
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="e1"></div>
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="e2"></div>
                        <div class="connect_point" data-id="e3"></div>
                    </div>
                    <svg class="connect_lines"></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="page page_2">
        <h3 lang="y">대응점끼리 이은 세 선분이 만나는 점을 찾아 점 ㅇ으로 표시해 보세요.​</h3>
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="figure_img_box click_figure_box">
            <div class="figure click_figure">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_08_SU/0004_content02.svg" alt="도형이미지">
              <div class="figure_triangle">
                <span class="txt_1" lang="y">ㄱ</span>
                <span class="txt_2" lang="y">ㄴ</span>
                <span class="txt_3" lang="y">ㄷ</span>
                <span class="txt_4" lang="y">ㄹ</span>
                <span class="txt_5" lang="y">ㅁ</span>
                <span class="txt_6" lang="y">ㅂ</span>
              </div>
              <!-- <div class="connect_point_box" data-connections='[]' data-answer-single='[{"x":188,"y":94}]'></div> -->
              <div class="boolean_wrap connect_point_box">
                <button class="point1" data-answer-single="true"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="page page_3">
        <h3 lang="y">점 ㅇ이 대칭의 중심인지 확인해 보세요​</h3>
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start pt_60">
          <div class="figure_img_box po_relative">
            <button class="btn_rotation"><span>회전버튼</span></button>
            <div class="figure_wrap">
              <div class="figure">
                <svg width="441" height="219" viewBox="0 0 441 219" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="img_ro">
                  <path d="M317.667 109.474L317.574 1H1.32812L123.709 109.474L123.771 217.917H440.048L317.667 109.474Z" stroke="#1D1D1B" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="figure_triangle">
                  <span class="txt_1" lang="y">ㄱ</span>
                  <span class="txt_2" lang="y">ㄴ</span>
                  <span class="txt_3" lang="y">ㄷ</span>
                  <span class="txt_4" lang="y">ㄹ</span>
                  <span class="txt_5" lang="y">ㅁ</span>
                  <span class="txt_6" lang="y">ㅂ</span>
                  <span class="txt_7" lang="y">ㅇ</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12 mt_20 f32b">
              <span lang="y">점 ㅇ이 대칭의 중심이</span>
  
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="맞습니다.">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value="맞습니다."></option>
                  <option value="아닙니다."></option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </article>
      <article class="page page_4">
        <h3 lang="y">선분 ㄱㅇ과 선분 ㄹㅇ, 선분 ㄴㅇ과 선분 ㅁㅇ, 선분 ㄷㅇ과 선분 ㅂㅇ의 길이를 각각 비교해 보세요.​</h3>
        <div class="input_area">
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col gap_30">
            <div class="select_group">
              <span>선분 ㄱㅇ 길이</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="=">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value=">">></option>
                  <option value="=">=</option>
                  <option value="<"><</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <span>선분 ㄹㅇ 길이</span>
            </div>
            <div class="select_group">
              <span>선분 ㄴㅇ 길이</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="=">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value=">">></option>
                  <option value="=">=</option>
                  <option value="<"><</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <span>선분 ㅁㅇ 길이</span>
            </div>
            <div class="select_group">
              <span>선분 ㄷㅇ 길이</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="=">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value=">">></option>
                  <option value="=">=</option>
                  <option value="<"><</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <span>선분 ㅂㅇ 길이</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="page page_5">
        <h3 lang="y">점대칭도형에서 대응점끼리 이은 선분과 대칭의 중심 사이의 관계에 대해 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.​</h3>
        <div class="ttext_area flex align_center justify_center">
          <div class="input_wrap mt_20 align_center justify_center flex1">
            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
            <div class="example_box">
              <p lang="y">점대칭도형에서 대칭의 중심은 대응점끼리 이은 선분을 똑같이 둘로 나눕니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="page page_6">
        <div class="summarize_wrap">
          <div class="summarize">
            <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
            <div>
              <span lang="y">점대칭도형에서 대칭의 중심은 대응점끼리</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span lang="y">이은 선분을</span>
              <button class="reveal_btn" lang="y">똑같이</button> 
              <span lang="y">둘로 나눕니다.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true" lang="y">제출</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>